3)🔥in the Rocky Mountains. (2006)

21 yr old Lebron on the 2nd night of a back to back cooked Utah. He dropped 50+ for the 3rd time in his young career as he had Utah’s bench amazed. When you have the Utah crowd cheering, you know it’s real.
